{"1138640":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Hometopia","steam_appid":1138640,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"detailed_description":"<h1>WISHLIST AND FOLLOW HOMETOPIA!<\/h1><p><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1138640\/extras\/wishlistandfollow2.gif?t=1659114013\" \/><\/p><br><h1>JOIN OUR OFFICIAL DISCORD<\/h1><p><a href=\"https:\/\/steamcommunity.com\/linkfilter\/?url=https:\/\/discord.gg\/fBczChD\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  ><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1138640\/extras\/Discord2.png?t=1659114013\" \/><\/a><\/p><br><h1>About the Game<\/h1><i>Build, design, and renovate beautiful homes across five unique neighborhoods, or freely build dream houses and neighborhoods from scratch alone or with friends online.<\/i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BUILD ENTIRE HOMES FROM SCRATCH - FOUNDATION TO ROOFTOPS<\/strong><\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1138640\/extras\/Gif_Dreamhouse_Build.gif?t=1659114013\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIRST PERSON OR OVERHEAD VIEW<\/strong><\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1138640\/extras\/Gif_exploreinfirstperson_600_6sec.gif?t=1659114013\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BUILD WITH OTHERS ONLINE<\/strong><\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1138640\/extras\/Gif_multiplayer.gif?t=1659114013\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CUSTOMIZE EVERYTHING<\/strong><\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1138640\/extras\/Gif_furniture_Paint.gif?t=1659114013\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GRID-LESS DESIGNING<\/strong><\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1138640\/extras\/Gif_gridlessPlacement.gif?t=1659114013\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>RENOVATE ENTIRE HOUSES<\/strong><\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1138640\/extras\/Gif_House_Reno.gif?t=1659114013\" \/><br><img src=\"https